✅ Fix (Clean + Stable)

✅ Step 1: Fix error key properly

const errorStateKey = `${errors.accuratelyReflects}-${errors.alternativeClassification}-${errors.taxDeclaration}`;

⸻

✅ Step 2: Update last error state

Add this after check:

